data.meta_description: Heading back to the earlier Mecklenburg Schwerin line, Duke John Albert, (brother of the formidable Grand Duchess Vlad) first married Princess Elisabeth of Saxe Weimar Eisenach in 1886. She's wearing a resplendent diamond and possibly emerald tiara, with an impressive central motif featuring nine emeralds in a diamond spray, rising from a diamond band. She died childless in 1908.
